import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { Project } from '../Interfaces/Interfaces'; import './ProjectView.css'; interface Ownprops { project: Project; setProject: (project: Project | null) => void; } function dateToString(date: Date): string { return `${date.getDate()}/${date.getMonth()}/${date.getFullYear()}`; } const ProjectView: React.FC = ({ project, setProject }) => { return (

{project.name}

Description

{project.description}

Contexte

{project.context}

Objectif

{project.goal}

Etapes

    {project.steps.map((step, index) => (

  • {step.name}

    Temps de travail en heure : {step.duration}

    XP(s) : {step.xp}

    • ))}

Temporalité

{dateToString(project.startDate)}

{dateToString(project.endDate)}

XP

{project.xp}

Nombre de participants

{project.workers}

Projet terminé

{project.isCompleted ? "Oui" : "Non"}

setProject(null)}> Retour
); } export default ProjectView;
